    Glyph Aquarium launcher icon — foreground layer.

    Renders a static snapshot of the aquarium: 4 small fish in school formation
    swimming above 3 seaweed stalks, all mapped onto the 25×25 glyph matrix grid.

    Coordinate system: cx = 18 + col*3,  cy = 18 + row*3
    Safe zone covers cols 0–24 / rows 0–24  (18dp to 90dp).

    smallFish sprite (3×7), center at col 3 / row 1:
      row -1:  _ _ 9 9 7 _ 4
      row  0:  9 9 1 1 9 9 1
      row +1:  _ _ 9 9 7 _ 4

    School centres (col, row):  fish1=(5,5)  fish2=(14,8)  fish3=(9,13)  fish4=(17,16)
    Seaweed stalks: col=3 rows18-24 | col=12 rows17-24 | col=22 rows19-24
-->
